org.gbif.api.vocabulary

Enum Language

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Language>
      • org.gbif.api.vocabulary.Language
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Language>

    public enum Language
extends Enum<Language>
    Enumeration for all ISO 639-1 language codes using 2 lower case letters. The enumeration maps to 3 letter codes and Locales.
    See Also:
    Wikipedia on ISO-639, Locale javadoc

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  Language.IsoSerializer
      Serializes the value in a 3 letter ISO format.
      static class  Language.LenientDeserializer
      Deserializes the value from a 3 letter ISO format or the enumeration name itself to maintain as much backwards compatibility as possible with e.g.
